Package: PCAoutlierRemover
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Outlier Removal from PCA of Population Genomic Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("James", "Hereward",
           email = "j.hereward@uq.edu.au",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Shiny gadget for identifying and removing outlier samples
    from PCA plots of population genomic data. Designed for ddRAD/SNP
    datasets filtered with SNPfiltR or similar workflows. Works directly
    from a genind object or a scores data frame. Drag a rectangle to
    brush-select samples, click to toggle individual points, switch
    between PC axes on the fly, and return the selected sample IDs to
    R for downstream filtering.
